{
  "texts": [
    "The data gathered from the official ontologies is open-source and available for download on their websites.",
    "To mirror the original format of the corpus, the list of monolingual English entities is formatted into a CONLL format with BIO scheme: [ENTITY, TAG].",
    "20% of the entities in the training, test, and evaluation sets have been replaced at random from the list corresponding to the tag.",
    "We attempted to replace the same number of entities for each tag to include a balanced number of new entities.",
    "7,161 entities were altered in the training set, 5,941 in the test set, and 2,267 in the evaluation set."
  ]
}